{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "fea4196c-cefa-44ea-b072-5a20e73a6bcb", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/fea4196c-cefa-44ea-b072-5a20e73a6bcb@1.pkg/1772597694402/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597695020", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/fea4196c-cefa-44ea-b072-5a20e73a6bcb@1.pkg/1772597694402/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597695020"}, "identifier": "fea4196c-cefa-44ea-b072-5a20e73a6bcb", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>本题考查 &ldquo;探问人生目标&rdquo; 中认识自我与规划人生的关系。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>A：课程帮助学生 &ldquo;认识自我优势、发掘潜能&rdquo;，进而 &ldquo;科学规划学业与未来生活&rdquo;，体现了在自我认知基础上明确人生方向，符合 &ldquo;探问人生目标&rdquo; 中人生目标需结合自身禀赋的知识点，A 正确；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>B：&ldquo;不必考虑其他兴趣发展&rdquo; 错误，全面发展既包括学业，也包括兴趣培养，二者并非对立；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>C：&ldquo;完全依据他人建议&rdquo; 忽视了自主规划的重要性，人生目标的确定应兼顾他人建议与自我判断；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>D：&ldquo;快速确定终身职业目标&rdquo; 不现实，成长是动态过程，目标可在探索中逐步明确，且 &ldquo;避免迷茫&rdquo; 过于绝对；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>答案选 A。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">（改编）</span><span>广东省教育厅印发《广东省中学生涯规划课程指导纲要（试行）》，将 &ldquo;生涯规划课程&rdquo; 纳入初高中课程，通过课程引导中学生认识自我优势、发掘潜能，科学规划学业与未来生活。这一课程有助于学生（ ）</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "（改编）广东省教育厅印发《广东省中学生涯规划课程指导纲要（试行）》，将 “生涯规划课程” 纳入初高中课程，通过课程引导中学生认识自我优势、发掘潜能，科学规划学业与未来生活。这一课程有助于学生（ ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "examples": {"responses": [], "feedbacks": [], "items": []}, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["A"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/fea4196c-cefa-44ea-b072-5a20e73a6bcb@1.pkg/item.json?v=1754984658505", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>在认识自我的基础上，逐步明确人生发展的方向</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>集中精力提升学业成绩，不必考虑其他兴趣发展</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>完全依据他人建议规划人生，减少自主选择的烦恼</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>快速确定终身职业目标，避免成长过程中的迷茫</span></p></div>"}], "prompt": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">（改编）</span><span>广东省教育厅印发《广东省中学生涯规划课程指导纲要（试行）》，将 &ldquo;生涯规划课程&rdquo; 纳入初高中课程，通过课程引导中学生认识自我优势、发掘潜能，科学规划学业与未来生活。这一课程有助于学生（ ）</span></p></div>", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalIm